{"tid":412653,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「年經」警告！月餅多食會致肥！","createTime":"2017-09-25T00:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T00:03:29.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"214f2873350ac117d1d18a165e20ae59182f2bdd","tid":412653,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:04:01.000Z","msg":"一個200克、傳統的雙黃蓮蓉月餅，熱量約有800卡路里，相等於4碗飯、15茶匙以上的砂糖、9茶匙油的脂肪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個200克的冰皮月餅熱量稍低，但也有700卡路里，相等於3碗飯的熱量、7茶匙油的脂肪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五仁月餅含多種果仁，如核桃、欖仁、杏仁，標榜高纖、健康的植物性脂肪，為健康人士追捧；但要注意，如在製作時，餡料是用蔗糖、肥豬肉或糖冬瓜的話，那就擺脫不了高油、高糖、高脂的黑名單。"},{"pid":"7d6a266f7f08666ada5e8182ccde41a0071dc2a7","tid":412653,"uid":64277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:35:46.000Z","msg":"好鍾意食雙黃白蓮蓉月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65ae991d71bf3cdcb5db8f2eb849a90cb4e5b89","tid":412653,"uid":1039,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:37:55.000Z","msg":"走蛋黃會唔會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66596f02c5b589190ea6e58485cf71b44a4df279","tid":412653,"uid":1247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:38:08.000Z","msg":"有時候真係食個黃"},{"pid":"a658fb0c279b609d315c76e30c7850fcf0fc8252","tid":412653,"uid":23170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:51:44.000Z","msg":"食五仁嘅話不如唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e51699f5453818f5ccc0255ac7aa4f442cfa71","tid":412653,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時候真係食個黃</blockquote><br />\n唔食黃不如買個唐餅啪算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38bdaa3dbbf397ba03751ed8e04a025c8479928","tid":412653,"uid":2950,"like":0,"di