,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"白飯多食都會致肥  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815cc4ebc7fbdf8d0b6a5656bd07c33764a4ce0a","tid":412653,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:22:48.000Z","msg":"世事都被佢看透了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08000cd2b775affefa1467c31b0d6c7879deb790","tid":412653,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶皇月餅呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奶皇仲撚肥 你睇下盒月餅個營養標籤就知<br />\n細細一個 係傳統/冰皮一半size kcal已經7xx-800...<br />\n我本身都好鍾意食 見到個標籤之後嚇親<br />\n依加唯有兩日食半個/1個 同埋食完狂做運動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb33b1ea2c9bc0c4ad7937360bc64c28753e608","tid":412653,"uid":45821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"五仁月餅真係狗也不屌<br />\n拎去餵狗都覺得係虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daaa85aa875854f454a2ebfd473247a64ab6073e","tid":412653,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五仁月餅真係狗也不屌<br />\n拎去餵狗都覺得係虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前讀中學有個同學拎左個番學校食 我食左1/4舊覺得好撚好食 之後買又覺得好撚難食 唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f123533ee533eaa11a7ab17e70886b1029d2643b","tid":412653,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:41:36.000Z","msg":"年年都有呢d新聞咖啦"},{"pid":"562232f1b54385e33c00d7ebe912c7de38d8f212","tid":412653,"uid":7466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>五仁月餅真係狗也不屌<br />\n拎去餵狗都覺得係虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea